spec_data.Name: mac-encheez
spec_data.Description:
mac-encheez provides a way to run a program such that it has a modified view
of the MAC addresses of the network interfaces of the computer.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 14 Oct 2017 04:06:46 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Run a program with a modified view of network MAC addresses
